---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import thumbsImage from "../assets/thumbs.jpg";
---

<div class="relative bg-white">
  <div
    class="relative h-80 overflow-hidden bg-pink-600 md:absolute md:left-0 md:h-full md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/2"
  >
    <Image src={thumbsImage} alt="Mums" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
  </div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8 lg:py-40">
    <div
      class="pl-6 pr-6 md:ml-auto md:w-2/3 md:pl-16 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-24 lg:pr-0 xl:pl-32"
    >
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-pink-400">Join Us</h2>
      <p
        class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-800 sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Together we are stronger!
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-7 text-gray-500">
        We cannot achieve our goals alone. We invite you to join us in our
        mission to uplift Romanian mothers. Whether through volunteering, making
        a donation, or spreading the word about our cause, your support can make
        a lasting impact on the lives of countless mothers and their children.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="mailto:contact@romanianmothers.org.uk"
          class="rounded-lg bg-pink-500 px-3.5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-pink-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-pink-500"
          >Join us</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
